\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">959</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱμάτων παλαιτέρων τ. μύσος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">send</tr_> one pollution <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in repayment</tr_> for another, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:650\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ch.\">Ch.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">650</biblScope> </bibl>(lyr., Lachm., for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τείνει</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">; ἀρᾶς τ. χρέος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:457\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">457</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (lyr.).--Constr.: </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n104040.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. of the thing paid or of the thing repaid (v. supr.). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n104040.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> less freq. c. dat., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κράατι τείσεις</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with</tr_> thy head, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:218\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.218</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ψυχῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:277\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bib